chr20.all.bam is the bam file that contains HiC data from our lab. 
chr20_step2_inference is the haplotype predictions

NA12878.chr20.hiseq.wgs.bwa.recal.bam is the genome sequencing data (from Depristo et al). The data is aligned to hg18 and is downloaded from ftp://ftp-trace.ncbi.nih.gov/1000genomes/ftp/technical/working/20101201_cg_NA12878/ and chr20 alone was extracted out.

====================
Simulation ReadMe

svpaths are located in simulations;
  totals are split into A,B

Read simulations are complicated.
WGS chr20 had 45835130 mapped + 695564 unmapped reads
HiC chr20 had  8739546 mapped

Each svpath (sim.chr20.<sim num>.bed)  implicates two haploid chromosomes A,B (a partitioning of deletions from svpath)
  - generate reads from each haploid chromsomes
     - sim.wgs (sim.chr20.<sim num>.<allele>.wgs.dat  
     - hic (sim.del-chr20_<sim num %03d>.<allele>.dat
  - convert reads from each haploid chromosome to ref position
     - sim.wgs (sim.chr20.<sim num>.<allele>.wgs.ref.dat)
     - hic (sim.del-chr20_<sim num %03d>.<allele>.ref.dat)
  - downsample reads to match real datasets (special for homozygous case)
     - sim.wgs (sim.chr20.<sim num>.<allele>.wgs.ref.<sampling>.dat
     - hic (sim.del-chr20_<sim num %03d>.<allele>.ref.<sampling>.dat
  - filter reads for only overlapping with chr20_step2_inference 
     - sim.wgs (sim.chr20.<sim num>.<allele>.wgs.ref.<sampling>.filt.dat
     - hic (sim.del-chr20_<sim num %03d>.<allele>.ref.<sampling>.filt.dat

Training Dataset:
Realistic Classes pA,pB,inc
  - p<allele> 
     sim.chr20.<sim num>.<allele>.bed 
     sim.chr20.<sim num>.wgs.ref.down4.dat
     sim.chr20.<sim num>.A.wgs.ref.down4.filt.dat
     sim.chr20.<sim num>.B.wgs.ref.down4.filt.dat
     sim.del-chr20.<sim num %03d>.A.ref.down2.filt.dat
     sim.del-chr20.<sim num %03d>.B.ref.down2.filt.dat
  - inc     
     sim.chr20.<sim num>.<allele>.bed 
     sim.chr20.<inc sim num>.wgs.ref.down4.dat
     sim.chr20.<inc sim num>.A.wgs.ref.down4.filt.dat
     sim.chr20.<inc sim num>.B.wgs.ref.down4.filt.dat
     sim.del-chr20.<inc sim num %03d>.A.ref.down2.filt.dat
     sim.del-chr20.<inc sim num %03d>.B.ref.down2.filt.dat
Realistic Classes p,inc
  - p
    combine tables for pA and pB
Realistic Classes pA,pB,homA,homB,inc
  - hom<allele>
     sim.chr20.<sim num>.<allele>.bed 
     sim.chr20.<sim num>.<allele>.wgs.ref.down2.dat
     sim.chr20.<sim num>.<allele>1.wgs.ref.down2.filt.dat
     sim.chr20.<sim num>.<allele>2.wgs.ref.down2.filt.dat
     sim.del-chr20.<sim num %03d>.<allele>1.ref.filt.dat
     sim.del-chr20.<sim num %03d>.<allele>2.ref.filt.dat

